    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just about being tired though. it's that nothing actually changes. it's the same patterns, the same mistakes, the same feeling of being nothing. i feel like i'm just running in place until i collapse. no matter how much i \"rest\" or \"reflect,\" the loop stays exactly the same. it's like it's hardwired into me.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
